 Please Enjoy.

-- HOW TO PLAY --

 Use your mouse!

-- ----------- --

 Instructions for compilation follow...

-- Desktop --

 Ensure libraylib.so.5.5/libglfw.so exists in your linker path.
 If you do not or cannot install raylib via your package manager:

git clone https://github.com/raysan5/raylib --depth=0
make -C raylib/src/ PLATFORM=PLATFORM_DESKTOP BUILD_MODE=RELEASE RAYLIB_LIBTYPE=SHARED install

git clone https://github.com/8e8m/meat --depth=0
cd meat
make run

-- Web --

 You must have emscripten installed:
 <https://emscripten.org/docs/getting_started/downloads.html>

 # Build emscripten
git clone https://github.com/emscripten-core/emsdk.git
cd emsdk
./emsdk install latest
./emsdk activate latest
source ./emsdk_env.sh
cd ../

 # Build the game
 # CWD .../meat/
git clone https://github.com/8e8m/meat --depth=0
cd meat
emmake make run

